trans-unit.source: An ellipse annotation can display text inside the ellipse, in addition to being displayed as an ellipse only.
trans-unit.target: Ellipsen merknaden kan vise teksten i ellipsen, i tillegg til å vises som en ellipsen bare.

trans-unit.source: You can therefore annotate using an ellipse or an ellipse with text inside it.
trans-unit.target: Du kan derfor Kommenter ellipsen og ellipsen med teksten i den.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This abstract property is used to get the name of each annotation type, such as a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LineAnnotation>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation>.
trans-unit.target: Abstrakt egenskapen brukes til å hente navnet på hver for merknadstypen som en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LineAnnotation>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation>, eller <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.EllipseAnnotation> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.RectangleAnnotation> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LineAnnotation>

trans-unit.source: This property is for internal use and should not be used.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er for intern bruk, og bør ikke brukes.
